Steps to Reproduce:

1.<script></script>内的js代码不能多行注释，如下
`  <!--export default {
    props:{
      showModal
    },
   methods:{
     de:function(){
       this.showModal = !this.showModal
     }
   }
  }-->`
![1](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/22283858/19886092/cbb46c74-a05c-11e6-9bb3-4f5e4e6d8069.png)

- VSCode Version: 1.7
- OS Version: OS X 10.11.6

Before formatting

```tsx
import * as React from "react";

export interface HelloProps { compiler: string; framework: string; }

export class Hello extends React.Component<HelloProps, {}> {
    render() {
        return <h1>Hello from {this.props.compiler} and {this.props.framework}!</h1>;
    }
}
```

After Document Format with 2 spaces:

```tsx
import * as React from "react";

export interface HelloProps { compiler: string; framework: string; }

export class Hello extends React.Component<HelloProps, {}> {
  render() {
    return <h1>Hello from {this.props.compiler}and {this.props.framework}!</h1>;
  }
}
```

The space between `} and` is gone after formatting.
